<p>We are pleased to announce that PMHC MDS Update v0.37.2 was released on June 1, 2020.</p>

<p>The following features have been implemented in the user management interface:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Filtering has been enabled on the Invites table</li>
</ul>

<p>The following features have been implemented in the data entry interface:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The Service Contact add and edit forms have been rearranged so that â€˜No Showâ€™ is after â€˜Service Contact Dateâ€™. The following fields are now pre-filled based on the value of â€˜No Showâ€™:
    <ul>
      <li>Service Contact - Type</li>
      <li>Service Contact - Postcode</li>
      <li>Service Contact - Modality</li>
      <li>Service Contact - Venue</li>
      <li>Service Contact - Duration</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>The following features have been implemented in the upload interface:</p>
<ul>
  <li>PHN users can now see all uploads for their PHN</li>
  <li>Data entered, but not saved before a timeout is now saved so that the data can be restored if the user logs back in within 15 minutes</li>
</ul>

<p>The following bug fixes have been implemented in the reports interface:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Corrected the B6 Option from â€˜Primary focus of treatment planâ€™ to â€˜Principal focus of treatment planâ€™</li>
  <li>Fixed a bug where the â€˜Requestâ€™ button was inactive and no error messages where shown when there was no active organisation with the reporting period</li>
</ul>

<p>The user guide has been updated to reflect these updates. It is available
at <a href="https://docs.pmhc-mds.com/projects/user-documentation/en/latest/" target="_blank">https://docs.pmhc-mds.com/projects/user-documentation/en/latest/</a>.</p>
